Dialogs.Dialog: Rinko
Oh, there's a very handsome man walking around right now.
...Hmm.
Ugh, you are boring. Don't you ever say, "You just look at me"？
Okay, if you want me to say it, then...
I can't do it. It doesn't suit you, so you shouldn't do it.
(Which one...)
Rinko
Hey. What would you do if a bad guy suddenly attacked Rinko right now？
Of course I will protect you with my body！
Hiya！
Ouch. What are you doing？
Game over. You need to raise your level more.
Rinko
Ah！ A cat just turned that corner.
I really like them. It's not that unusual, is it？
...Even if they are about the size of an adult？
Is that... really a cat？
Rinko
Ah, watch out！
What！？
Ahh.
What's the matter？
If you step off the white line, you're out. Didn't we play like that in the old days？
(Are you in grade school...)
Rinko
Oh, hey, that old building over there. Is it called a Western-style building？
What about it？
They say there is some kind of jealous girl spirit and if a couple passes in front of it, they will be cursed.
...Seriously？ Do you want to take a detour？
It's okay, I'm lying. Are you really that scared of it？
Rinko
I wonder where this road straight ahead leads to.
Um, was it in front of the station？
Be more literary.
Literary？ Um... "Our future is connected！"
Oh, that cloud is weirdly shaped...
...Listen to me.
Rinko
Oh... Hey, what about men who wear makeup？
Hmm, ah, that guy... isn't he member of a band？
Shortsighted. Well, it sounds like it.
Don't you think so？ Didn't you have a favorite musician who wears makeup ▲小早川＊▲？
I know there are some people who have... but that's totally different from this.
Rinko
Wow, a big dog.
I think you can get on it, ▲小早川＊▲.
Did you say something？
I didn't say anything.
...Can I really ride it？
Rinko
There's another couple making out outside...
Wow, it's true... But you said "again"？
I feel like I've been encountering them a lot lately. Hah, public disorder.
So, you're of the school that doesn't kiss outside, huh... is that right ▲小早川＊▲？
Shut up！
Rinko
Whoa！
What's up？
The mannequins in the show window appear to have moved...
Ah, seriously... That's...
Ah, geez, come on. Hurry up, let's go.
Rinko
Did you hear a guitar just now？ I wonder if they are practicing somewhere.
Really？ I didn't hear it...
Rinko hasn't touched one in a while...
Oh, I didn't know you had one.
Yeah, I just have one. Hah, I wonder if touching it will dent it again...
Rinko
Prince on a white horse, eh...
Hmm？ Oh, it's an ad. "Introducing your very own prince on a white horse". That's a great catchphrase.
Why a white horse？
Who knows, maybe because it's cool.
Then wouldn't a tiger or something be cooler？ A prince riding a white tiger.
Cool, but scary...
It's about to go down hill.
Rinko
When you're walking up a hill, don't you imagine a rock rolling down？
That seems dangerous.
Really？ That sounds like fun. It's entertainment.
(Are you having fun...？)
Rinko
You know those commercials that often show a couple walking hand in hand？
The have no choice, you know.
What do you mean？
Aren't they supposed to hold hands？
I didn't say that. If that's what you want to do, fine.
Rinko
Ugh...
What's the matter？ It's not such a scary dog, is it？
That's a face that doesn't go well with Rinko. It's not a good idea to get close to something like that.
(How can you know that...)
Rinko
You know, down the road, there's always a dog that barks at people passing by.
Yeah, they're chained up, but I feel like they're going to jump on me at any moment.
I was worried about when that chain would break. And when it does, you're going to help me, okay？
Yeah, leave it to me！
Thanks. Keep Rinko close enough so she can get away.
(So I'm the decoy...)
Rinko
You know, when I was little, I used to think potato chips were leaves.
Huh？
The shape looks like a leaf. That's why I though there was a tree like that...
Haha, so there are many different flavors of trees.
Yeah, consomme or seaweed. Children often come up with such things.
Rinko
Someone once told me that moving around is a waste of time, but a walk is worth it.
Hmm, what do you mean？
Moving is about getting to a destination, though. Walking is about walking itself, isn't it？
I see. Walking can be fun and a break in itself, right？
So, now it's a walk. Come on, talk about something fun.
Oh, they are telling fortunes on the street. Would you like to try？
Rinko
Nope, that's fine. I'm not interested.
Hmm？

I don't care if it's in a magazine or on TV, but in a fortune-telling session like that, where you are looking the customer in the face, it's probably better to say only good things, for business purposes.
Well, maybe so.
Or, conversely, they could stir up anxiety and bring in business.
(You're a realist...)
Rinko
Oh, that was close.
...Ouch.
Are you okay？ It's because you're not paying attention.
The branch was popping out？ I didn't notice.
It's not because you're staring at Rinko. You have to walk looking forward.
Rinko
Did you know that down the road, there is a meeting place for feral cats？
Heh, I didn't know there was such a thing. Don't you want to go？
It's okay. I don't want to disturb them, so I just watch them from afar from time to time.
That's why you have to be careful.
Yes. It would be bad if I stepped into their private life.
Rinko
Do you refer to some kind of dating manual？
Yes... I might glance at it once in a while.
It's okay if it's just a glimpse, but what's important is originality, right？
(I'll be careful.)
Rinko
Ah... that surprised me.
What's wrong？
For a moment, I thought I had dropped my wallet.
That's dangerous.
Yeah. Hey, keep an eye on Rinko so she doesn't drop things.
It's fine, but... take care of yourself first.
Rinko
They say there are three people in the world who look like you.
I've heard that a lot, but I've never actually seen one.
But look, there's a girl over there who looks just like Rinko...
What！？ Where！
It was a joke. I don't know why I'm so obsessed with it.
(I'd like to see that.)
Rinko
Hey, what do you think of girls who play instruments？
There are many kinds of instruments, but... sounds good, neat, and cool.
...I know, Rinko agrees.
Are you going to try it？
...No. One taste of despair like that is enough.
(It's that serious...)
Rinko
I feel like my rock-paper- scissors has gotten weaker lately.
What do you mean with losing power...
rock-paper！
Eh！ Why so suddenly！？
...I better stop. If I lose again here, I'll lose even more confidence.
Rinko
I need to change my earphones soon. They go bad sometimes.
Have you decided which ones you're going to buy？
No, not yet. My dad knows a lot about that kind of stuff...
Then why don't you ask him？
I refuse. He knows too much, and talks too much.
Rinko
Hey. Can I see your palm？
I didn't know you had such special skills, ▲小早川＊▲.
Self-study. I read a book on palmistry in the library and found it surprisingly interesting.
(Is that all...？)
Yeah, this shows a phase of not being able to get away from Rinko... Hehe.
Rinko
The sun rises in the east, right？ What do you think would happen if it rose in the west？
What's going to happen... I think the sun will start setting in the east.
Well, that's true... Isn't there something more？ Don't you think we'll be in a lot of trouble！？
Hmm, like what？
Well... maybe more people will become left-handed！
(I think I understand...)
Rinko
When we walk around like this, sometimes it's hard to have a conversation.
Do you have any topics to talk about...？
No, I don't. I don't want to say something weird on the spur of the moment, but I also don't want to bore you with my silence...
You had such a cute idea, ▲小早川＊▲.
I'll tell you what, shut up. I made a mistake mentioning this.
Rinko
It's kind of unreasonable.
What's wrong？ Did I do something？
When we walk side by side like this, you look down on me, and I don't like that.
It can't be helped. There is a height difference.
I'm not convinced. Try walking with your knees bent today.
(That's absurd...)
Rinko
I want to fly.
...Do your best.
Because then I wouldn't have to walk around with you looking down on me. On the contrary, I will look down on you from far above.
It can't be helped, the height difference... but then you wouldn't be able to wear skirts, would you？
Skirts？ ...Idiot！
Rinko
When it comes to eating, it's not so much where you eat or what you eat, but who you eat with, isn't it？
Family members, lover？
That's right. If you are with your loved one, even a family restaurant is enough.
Oh, don't make fun of the family restaurants, okay？
Yes, yes. Anyway, I don't mind eating with you.
Rinko
Huh, is that a soccer ball？
Boy
Excuse me. Can you get that for me！？
All right, here we go！！
Thank you very much！
I see, you can do it.
Well, at least this much.
Rinko
What do you use as your cell phone's standby screen？
Um... it's a secret.
Hmm, maybe it's a picture of Rinko？
Who knows. Do you have a picture of me, ▲小早川＊▲！？
Too bad, it's a daily cat picture.
Rinko
There's a lot of danger out there.
For example？
Objects fall and fly, thugs attack, cars and bicycles.
Why are you talking about that？
I wondered how much danger this boyfriend of mine would protect me from.
I'll do my best...
Rinko
Ah, the lover's link.
Ah, wait they are both girls.
Sisters, I guess. They're so close.
Yeah, that makes me smile.
Rinko also likes to walk hand in hand with her little brother.
Rinko
Ah...
My bad. That was a little fast.
Not much. It's fine.
It's okay, let's go slowly.
...Yes.
Rinko
Hey. How's the weather forecast this morning？
I think the skies will be okay for any activity today.
Hmm.
If it rains, it might not be a bad idea to take shelter from the rain together.
Yeah... might be good. I'd rather have it rain. Hehe.
Rinko
Shucks... it's homeroom.
It's not like we're doing anything wrong, and it's okay if they find us, right？
Oh, I see. What a good conditioned reflex.
(So that's why you're often pissed off.)
Rinko
Whoa！ ...You're going too fast！ I'm gonna kick you！
Don't stare at me like that. What if it's someone scary？
I don't think so... Huh, I wonder if an exchange like that happened.
Yes, before we started dating. At the arcade.
Seems like it... Hehe.
Rinko
What is that... a samurai？
What？ I don't see him？
It turned right away. He had a chonmage and a sword in his hand.
Is it a photo shoot？ But then again, there's no one like that around...
Maybe it was a time slip？
(No way...)
Rinko
It's been a while since I listened to J-Pop properly.
Have your tastes changed？
No way. It's called a compromise from Rinko's side.
Heh, how did it go？
It wasn't bad because my dad recommended it... but the vocalist was kinda weak...
Rinko
My parents bought me a stuffed animal as a souvenir from an overseas business trip.
Stuffed animal？ Oh, a cat, ▲小早川＊▲？
Nope. It's a stuffed animal based on a local folk tale to ward off evil. I don't even know what kind of animal it is, and it's kind of hard to wake up...
(Stuffed animal to ward off evil...)
Rinko
Do you enjoy dating Rinko？
It's obvious, why do you ask？
Hehe, sometimes I feel like asking. It's called regular check.
Rinko
Amazing, there's a magical girl. Look, that girl.
Oh, a set of impersonators, huh？ Even with a walking stick.
Hmmm, she's cute. My little brother is cute, but a little sister would be nice too.
She's really cute, with her frilly fluttery hair.
...I forgot, you're a lolicon, right？
No, I'm not！
Rinko
Do you know the story of the "Monster of Towano City"？
Like an urban legend？
Something like that. They said he roams the neighborhood wearing a mask and cape.
What's the reason...？
Who knows？ If you're lucky enough to see him, he'll give you candy.
(Isn't that something a granny would do...)
Rinko
Hey. Why do men like to sleep on knee pillows？
I know not all men are like that, but, well, I admire them.
Hmmm, the boys in my class were getting excited... I see.
(You giving a knee pillow？ No way, ▲小早川＊▲...)
Ah, puddles.
Rinko
When you find a puddle, don't you feel an sudden urge to jump in it？
Especially when you're a kid.
Don't treat me like a child. Geezer！
(I didn't mean to...)
Rinko
A friend of mine was complaining about her boyfriend, saying they've been in a dating rut lately.
In a rut... huh. Do you think we're like that, ▲小早川＊▲？
I don't think so. That's not necessarily a bad thing.
Is that so？
It's not that I'm getting used to it. That's the next stage.
I see.
Rinko
That bamboo grove over there. It was always dark, and I was so scared when I was little that I always ran past it.
I see, and now？
I'm a high school student.
Haha, yeah.
If it was at night, I don't know...
Rinko
When you notice that your eye level has changed, you feel like you've grown, don't you？
The view changes, doesn't it？
These fences, too, seemed so high when I was little...
(For you, I'd say those fences are still high, ▲小早川＊▲...)
I can't hear you, but I can hear your heart.
(Esper...)
Rinko
...The song the guy we just passed by was listening, was from Killer Bambies.
You can tell a lot just by the acoustic noise.
Of course, I'm a fan.
If it was your voice, I would be confident that I could tell just from the sound leakage, ▲小早川＊▲.
...You don't say！
Rinko
Wow, amazing dress.
Hmm, what do you mean？
A woman who passed there. Her dress was like a ball gown.
Heh, in a place like this？
Yeah, it was something like Versailles！ Like that.
(I wonder what the event is...)
Rinko
Dating means walking, right？
I understand. Sometimes I wonder why we walk so much.
It's not that I don't like it.
That's part of dating, right？
Yes. Then you and Rinko will walk smoothly, too.
Rinko
Black luxury cars are so intimidating.
Oh, it's stopped. Mr. President！ Or something like that.
I'd love to kick a car like that someday.
Why would you do that！
It's like, "Oh, this is so cool," you know？ It's like being anti-system.
(Dangerous... Well, I don't think she's actually going to do it.)
Rinko
There was a poster of a lost cat put again, right？
Yes... Oh, it's posted again. I bet the owner is desperate to find it.
I pray that this little guy makes it back to his owner safely！
Rinko
That baby in the stroller is adorable.
Oh, really. You're smiling.
I love babies～. I wonder mom and dad won't make a baby.
...Why don't you ask？
That's okay, I might embarrass myself.
Rinko
Ah, puddles.
Whoa！？
It's because you're not paying attention.
...Ah, my shoes got a little wet.
It's fine to be crazy about your girlfriend, but look ahead while you walk.
Rinko
Oh, there's a new book out.
Ah, bookstore pop-ups. That's a bestselling author, you read those too？
Well, just in case. I don't like feeling chained.
As expected of a Library Committee member！
You too, you know.
Rinko
What's with that crowd？
...There's also a camera. Must be filming a drama or something.
That's what they do around here.
Want to take a look？
It's fine. I don't wanna see.
Hara
Oh, Rinko. On a date？
Rinko
...Well, sort of.
That girl is your friend, right？
Yeah.
You were rather curt in that regard.
I'm on good terms with her. When I'm seen with you... you know.
That guitar we saw on display at the music store earlier... you've been looking at it for a while, haven't you？
Rinko
Yeah, God.Mt model. The one that is a complete replica of the guitar he used.
Wow, there's that kind of thing too. Is that what you want？
It's too expensive and I can't afford it. It doesn't matter if Rinko has it in the first place.
Well, you have to play it.
But when I pass by that store, I'll be sure to take a look at it.
(I heard that somewhere...)
Rinko
Ah, another new convenience store.
That's a lot these days. There's a condo building nearby, so there's that. It's changing fast...
Well, if it makes it more convenient, so be it.
Don't you feel sad when the town you used to live in changes？
But that doesn't mean the memories are gone. So that's fine.
Rinko
Movers. Maybe an apartment there.
New apartments？
Yes. According to my parents, there are many young couples in that apartment.
A young couple, huh？ Then maybe there will be more babies and it will get noisy.
Ugh, that sounds like a lot of work...
Rinko
According to Rinko's research. It seems that many girls like to have their heads patted.
Hmm, that's a pretty brave move from the boys.
Well, it's not something you want anyone to do to you.
I guess so. By the way, are you among those girls, ▲小早川＊▲？
Who knows. Rinko doesn't want to fit into the category of so-called "common girls".
(So you're an special girl, ▲小早川＊▲...)
Rinko
...Kya！ Um, hmm...
What's wrong？
A little insect crossed in front of me.
Ah, you don't like them？
I hate them more than I dislike them. Even if I didn't, I would be shocked if one suddenly crossed in front of me.
Rinko
Don't you think women are at a disadvantage？
That's out of the blue. What's up？
You know how much time and effort it takes to get ready for a date？ Clothes, hair, and many more...
Hmm, sure is a lot of work！
Whose fault is it！？
(...Mine？)
Rinko
There is a convertible parked.
That's true. I guess you can see the interior.
I wonder what's going on with security and such.
It depends on the weather, too.
It's a cool car, but it looks like a lot of work.
Like a girlfriend who is cute, but needs a lot of attention？
I was trying to be nice！
Rinko
It's good to be so casual with your girlfriend that others don't even notice.
Hmm？ Well, maybe so.
You naturally move closer to the side of the road, you know？
Really？ Haha, that's kind of embarrassing.
Don't get carried away. Rinko found out, so you're disqualified. You have to do it so that she doesn't notice.
(That's a hard one...)
Rinko
...Urgh.
Are you okay！？
I just tripped a little, that's all. You worry too much.
Because you don't look ahead and walk properly... Whoa.
We both have to be careful.
Rinko
When you were a child, did you sing while walking？
Ah, I think I did once in a while. What about you, ▲小早川＊▲？
I don't remember, but I heard I used to sing a lot when I was a little girl.
Heh. No way, have you been into punk since then？
No way. Mama taught me nursery rhymes and songs from cartoons I was watching at the time.
Well, of course.
Rinko
Are you okay？ You're going too fast！
I can hear you, you know.
I'm worried, that's all.
It's okay... I'm not going to get mad at you if you get mad at me first.
Hehe, thanks.
Rinko
Ah... I might not have charged my phone.
Are you about to run out？ Want to find a store and recharge it?？
...It's fine. If it cuts out, it cuts out.
Are you sure？
Yeah, I'm with you, so you won't be calling me. So that's fine.
Rinko
That bookstore is closing.
Individuals can't compete with large stores.
Big bookstores are handy, but I don't mind the vibe of a small store either...
Rinko
Ah... something smells good. I wonder if it's freshly baked bread...
Ah, a mobile vending van. Looks like it's pretty popular.
This wafting sweet scent. I can see why it's so popular.
Want to buy some？
Hmm... I'll pass on getting in line. Another time.
Rinko
Flying sneakers.
What？
Oh, the kid just flew off his shoes.
That's so innocent.
Sounds like fun though.
Why don't you go join them？ Maybe the geezer would like to be a child again once in a while？
Though we're only a year apart！
Rinko
What's with the crowd？
A supermarket's big discount？
That was it？ The power of housewives is amazing, by the way.
Even you might become a housewife, you know, ▲小早川＊▲？
...No can do. At least I can't go in there.
Rinko
Someone is reading a book while walking. Dexterous.
That's more dangerous than dexterous.
I would like to read a book calmly, but given the busyness of today's world, it is inevitable that I would have to do something while reading.
You often reads books while listening to music, ▲小早川＊▲.
That's the basics. So, when I hear the song, I match it with the contents of the book, or conversely, when I see the title of the book, the song plays in my head, which is interesting.
Rinko
Was there ever a time when you didn't want your friends to see you with your parents？
Yes, maybe it was in upper elementary school.
I wonder if it's like measles. It's gone before you know it.
Is it like an awakening of independence, or something like that？
Maybe so. Like, "I'm fine on my own！" There's no way that's true.
Rinko
That mini car is cute. Was it a British one？
Seems like it.
I'm not that interested in cars, but if I had to drive one, it would be like that.
Heh. Somehow I thought you would like it cool.
I think it's better to be as charming as that. And it's nice that it's from England.
Rinko
They are doing road construction, I wonder if we can get through.
It looks like we can make it, but it's turning to mud. Should we take the long way around？
Okay, I'll walk carefully. If you want, do you want me to give you a piggyback ride？
Eh！？ Hmm, well, if you're not ashamed of it, then hop on, ▲小早川＊▲.
Of course I'm ashamed. I was just kidding.
Rinko
Did you hear they found a cat with a human face on the road up ahead？
Human face... I'm sorry, but that's a tad creepy, ▲小早川＊▲.
No, as I said, Rinko does not think it's cute either...
Haha, right...
I just imagined it, it's too scary...
Ah, an UFO！
Rinko
Yeah, sure.
I'm telling the truth！ ...What's that, a balloon？
Told ya. And I hate UFOs because I have bad memories of them.
What kind？
When I had a fight with my father a long time ago, I threw his treasured records out the window saying, "UFO！" He got mad at me.
(Well that much is clear...)
Rinko
I wonder if you and Rinko normally walk too much.
What's normal？
Isn't there a more lovely way to walk？
Hmm, for example？
For example... think for yourself.
(I think you brought this on yourself～.)
Rinko
Ah... I forgot to give water to Tama.
Tama...？ Oh, your cactus, right？
Yes. What if it dies...
Don't you think a cactus would be fine？
Yeah, but I'll call my mom just in case.
Rinko
Come to think of it, when did they start selling oden at convenience stores all year round？
Now that you mention it, they're losing their sense of seasons.
Maybe one day there will be shaved ice in the winter.
(That's not gonna happen...)
Rinko
Elementary school children gather to play games.
Don't you play mobile games ▲小早川＊▲？
I do it, but it's outside. Rinko's mobile games are non-mobile games.
What's with that？
Rinko
It's difficult to be fashionable on your feet, isn't it？
Is that so？
Because, you know, functionality is also important. Dating involves a lot of walking.
Ah, I understand.
There are also those hardships, I mean.
Rinko
I feel like the flyers they hand out on the street, if you accept them, you lose.
...Really？
Because, you know, what if I'm not interested at all？
I guess you have to throw it away.
If that happens, it's just trash. And if there's no trash can nearby, it's just a hindrance. That's why Rinko won't accept them.
Rinko
A website run by an info magazine introduced a spell that if two lovers hold hands and cross the street with their eyes closed, they will be happy.
That's too dangerous！
Yeah, that's why it was immediately complained about and removed. But it seems to have developed a cult following.
Was it counterproductive？
I hope it goes out of business before anyone gets hurt.
Rinko
I heard there is a ghost story about a cat lady. A common urban legend.
I see, is it a woman with only a cat face？
No, the opposite. They say her body is a bipedal cat and her face is an immensely beautiful woman.
...What a weird legend.
In short, they look like a human wearing a costume with only the headdress removed.
(That's just a beautiful woman in a costume...)
Rinko
Oh, a cat！
Oh, she's gone. That's too bad.
It's fine, it's so much more noble and cooler than a girl who gets lonely easily.
Is that how it works？
That's the way it is. That's the right way to be a cat.
Rinko
Ah, smoke...
What is it, a chimney？
When I see something like that, I kind of want to track down the source.
Oh, you want to try it？
...I pass. I tried to do that in the past, but those things are surprisingly far away and I never get close.
Rinko
Do you think you and Rinko look like lovers now？
Of course we look like that.
But my friend told me that we are like brother and sister.
Really？ Siblings at this age don't go out together.
That's not the point. You don't understand.
Rinko
I feel like I'm getting a good deal when the weather is nice on our date.
Yeah, and laundry day！
Hah, you're getting all domestic now. Rinko doesn't do her own laundry, so I don't really know.
Haha, help your mom out once in a while！
I'll think about it, because it's frustrating to be left in the shoes of a senpai in life.
Rinko
Do you think there is less trash on the streets in Towano City？ How does it compare to where you used to live？
Oh, if you ask me, maybe.
Well, that's a good thing. It feels good, and the attention to detail is proof that the social system is working well.
(You think that much about garbage on the road！)
Rinko
Oh, butterflies？
Hmm, isn't that a moth？
Ugh... why do I get such a different impression from butterflies and moths？
Yes, it's a nice nuisance for moths.
"Come on out, you're in charge！" Or something like that.
Rinko
What's the rush？
You think？
That's what I feel like.
If you say so, it must be so. All right, let's go ▲小早川＊▲♪
Yes, yes.
Rinko
I saw some chalk graffiti on the road earlier.
Yeah, I haven't seen that in a while.
Feels like I'm getting itchy for some mischief！
Don't do it. We're high school students.
I know. Let me doodle on your face. Wouldn't that be nice？
(How can that be！)
